---
---

<section class="bg-surface-container-low py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8">
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground lg:text-4xl">
        Keunggulan Operasional & Strategis
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-6 max-w-2xl text-muted-foreground">
        Lebih dari sekadar pengangkutan, kami memberikan jaminan kepatuhan regulasi dan mitigasi risiko operasional menyeluruh untuk bisnis Anda.
      </p>
      <div class="mx-auto h-1 w-20 rounded-full bg-primary"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div
        class="group flex flex-col gap-3 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 shadow-xs ring-1 ring-foreground/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-base font-bold">Legalitas Mutlak & Izin KLHK</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Kepastian hukum operasional Anda terjamin dengan izin pengangkutan resmi dari KLHK dan Kemenhub yang selalu aktif.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group flex flex-col gap-3 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 shadow-xs ring-1 ring-foreground/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"/><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-base font-bold">Mitigasi Risiko & Keamanan Total</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Prosedur pengangkutan ketat yang meminimalisir risiko insiden lingkungan dan melindungi reputasi bisnis Anda.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group flex flex-col gap-3 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 shadow-xs ring-1 ring-foreground/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-base font-bold">Expertise & Sertifikasi K3/B3</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Operator dan pengemudi profesional yang telah melewati sertifikasi teknis penanganan limbah B3 dan standar K3 tinggi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="group flex flex-col gap-3 overflow-hidden rounded-xl bg-card p-6 shadow-xs ring-1 ring-foreground/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg"
      >
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary/10">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 w-6 text-primary"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"/><path d="M7 16h8"/><path d="M7 11h12"/><path d="M7 6h3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading text-base font-bold">Transparansi & Integrasi FESTRONIK</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Sistem manifest elektronik yang terintegrasi langsung dengan KLHK untuk pelaporan yang akurat, cepat, dan transparan.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
